<paragraph id="8BEA37705570FF9C528DBFE1FC2FFABD" blockId="26.[189,1399,1272,1334]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">
The new species is named after David Gonzales (Saint-Laurent-du-Pape, 
<collectingCountry id="F34277E05570FF9C5604BFE0FB32FA98" box="[1076,1160,1273,1299]" name="France" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">France</collectingCountry>
), who made a great contribution to the 
<taxonomicName id="4C554CF35570FF9C53ACBE05FDF9FABD" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[412,579,1308,1334]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Tenebrionidae</taxonomicName>
of the New and Old Worlds.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
